  27:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****   ==============================================================================
  28:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****   [..] The Flexible memory controller (FSMC) includes following memory controllers:
  29:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        (+) The NOR/PSRAM memory controller
  30:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        (+) The NAND/PC Card memory controller
  31:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c **** 
ARM GAS  C:\Users\84759\AppData\Local\Temp\cc7j0lhw.s 			page 2


  32:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****   [..] The FSMC functional block makes the interface with synchronous and asynchronous static
  33:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        memories and 16-bit PC memory cards. Its main purposes are:
  34:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        (+) to translate AHB transactions into the appropriate external device protocol
  35:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        (+) to meet the access time requirements of the external memory devices
  36:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c **** 
  37:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****   [..] All external memories share the addresses, data and control signals with the controller.
  38:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        Each external device is accessed by means of a unique Chip Select. The FSMC performs
  39:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        only one access at a time to an external device.
  40:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****        The main features of the FSMC controller are the following:
  41:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****         (+) Interface with static-memory mapped devices including:
  42:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****            (++) Static random access memory (SRAM)
  43:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****            (++) Read-only memory (ROM)
  44:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****            (++) NOR Flash memory/OneNAND Flash memory
  45:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****            (++) PSRAM (4 memory banks)
  46:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****            (++) 16-bit PC Card compatible devices
  47:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****            (++) Two banks of NAND Flash memory with ECC hardware to check up to 8 Kbytes of
  48:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****                 data
  49:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****         (+) Independent Chip Select control for each memory bank
  50:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****         (+) Independent configuration for each memory bank
  51:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c **** 
  52:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_ll_fsmc.c ****   @endverbatim
